product.title: Custom Colored Acrylic
product.body_html:
Colored Acrylic

Acrylic is commonly used for boxes/displays, signage, windows, aquariums, sneeze guards, and more! It is manufactured in a wide range of colors and is easily machinable, making it a great option for artistic purposes. Its versatility, durability, and aesthetic properties make it a popular choice in many industries.

Cutting & Sizing

All Cut To Size orders are cut on our 10′ CNC panel saw and may have a cutting tolerance of +/- .060″. If you have a tighter tolerance than +/- .060″ please give us a call.

Our sizing online is restricted to 48″ x 96″ sheets. If you would like to place an order for an oversized sheet please give us a call.

Edge Finish Options

  • Fingersafe: Lightly Softened Edges
  • Sanded: Removes Saw Marks, Soft Edges and Corners
  • Polished: Adds Smooth Glossy Edge
  • Sand & Buff: Perfect Edge Finish with no imperfections. Please call store for more detail. NOT AVAILABLE ONLINE.

Expected Turnaround Time

Turnaround Times vary based on order size and edge finish, but most order have a turnaround time of 1 to 3 business days.
